# Phase 1 is a fully static site — no environment variables required.
# Just `npm install && npm run dev`, or push to Vercel and deploy.
#
# Contact / newsletter submissions are logged to Vercel Runtime Logs.
# Find them in the Vercel dashboard → your project → Logs, filtered by
# `[contact-form]` or `[newsletter-signup]`.
#
# Phase 2 (backend) will reintroduce a database and add these vars —
# see the `phase-2-backend` branch for the previous working version.
